high_descs: Back up from the shelves, turn right, turn left to face the shelves.
Pick up black rag from the floor.
Approach the piece of furniture with shelves.
Put the rag on the right hand bottom shelf above where it was on the floor.
Look at the rags on the floor.
Pick up the yellow rag from the floor.
Approach the piece of furniture with shelves.
Put the yellow cloth on top of the black one.
anns.task_desc: Put two rags, yellow and black, on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the wall, then turn left walk forward, look down at the rags on the ground.
Pick up the black rag off of the ground.
Look up at the shelving unit on the wall in front of you.
Put the black rag in the middle of the bottom right shelf.
Look down at the ground where the rags are.
Pick up the yellow rag off of the ground.
Look back up at the shelving unit on the wall.
Put the yellow rag on the bottom right shelf on top of the black rag.
anns.task_desc: Move two rags to a shelf.

high_descs: Turn and go to the shelves.
Pick up a rag on the floor by the shelves.
Go to the shelves.
Put the rag on the shelves.
Go to the shelves.
Pick up a rag on the floor
Go to the shelves.
Put the rag on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put two rags on the floor on the shelves.
